Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.35,0:00:06.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:08.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.87,0:00:16.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.24,0:00:26.54,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We've left the established course
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, we're rowing straight toward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The borderline between the sky and the ocean
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:41.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,In the dark depths of the ocean,\Nadventure holds its breath
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.74,0:00:48.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have a good time just imagining it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:53.23,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Travel across the oceans of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.25,0:00:55.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellow a battle cry
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Once your heart feels refreshed,\Nlet the signal to set sail ring out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.58,0:01:13.01,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,"That feeling" I get when embarking
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:16.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something I hope to remember always
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.23,0:01:21.76,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can, I won't be afraid of anything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:27.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,With our pulses racing, let's go on a trip now
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.99,0:01:35.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shy hearts engrave the rhythm of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.04,0:01:39.15,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.17,0:01:41.77,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.79,0:01:46.13,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.15,0:01:48.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Life is "Adventurous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.52,0:01:52.21,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Be aware it's "Dangerous"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:53.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's gonna be "One of us"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And a trip goes on because
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.04,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,We da pirate of the "Mass"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.06,0:01:58.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,To the West, To the East
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.98,0:02:00.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Gotta find my way, Sail away
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.59,0:02:01.74,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,All the way to "One piece"!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.76,0:02:06.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuff a dream into your empty chest
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,And spread your wings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.20,0:02:12.56,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,If the wind blowing through\Nthem dyes your heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:14.98,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's press forward
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:19.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Snatch up the treasure here and there
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.11,0:02:21.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,While laughing out loud
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.49,0:02:25.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,As we dash by like a noisy party
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.90,0:02:32.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Make some waves...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.81,0:02:37.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.04,0:02:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gold Roger, the King of the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.75,0:02:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once attained everything\Nthis world has to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.86,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The words he uttered just before his death
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.21,0:02:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drove people around the world to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My treasure? If you want it, you can have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:58.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Find it! I left everything\Nthis world has to offer there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:03.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so men rushed onto the\NGrand Line in pursuit of romanticism!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has truly entered a Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.36,0:03:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This shadow will bring me one step closer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.95,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to becoming the King of the Pirates, Hogback!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.28,0:03:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a decade since we first met.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I put all of my prowess into creating\NNo. 900 for a day such as this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.28,0:03:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that shadow in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm certain it'll become the\Nmost powerful zombie in history!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.94,0:03:35.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be a great asset!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.78,0:03:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The day I become the world's\N"King of the Grave" is close at hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can practically see the day I turn\Nthe cute critters of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.53,0:03:49.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,into zombies and make them\Nserve me in my dream kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heave, ho! Heave, ho! Heave, ho!\NHeave, ho! Heave, ho!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy!\N--Stupid! Don't pop out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.95,0:03:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't die just because they took his shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.58,0:03:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:03:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.39,0:04:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, guys, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.89,0:04:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.83,0:04:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The zombies' weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is their weakness? What exactly is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.42,0:04:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To reiterate, please stuff salt into\Na zombie's mouth to defeat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the trick! Even for this\Nbag of bones, that's a snap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.18,0:04:23.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Snap! Snap! Snap!\N--But Brook...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.26,0:04:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so knowledgeable\Nabout the zombies and this island?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.88,0:04:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has to do with when I lost\Nmy shadow five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.72,0:04:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, they sent me back out to drift at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, I was able to\Nturn back by the time I awoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thus I returned to the island and fought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But in the end, I lost miserably.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you'll have to pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a hurry. Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On top of everything you've told us,\Nanswer this one question before you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.55,0:05:13.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.68,0:05:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw his corpse in the Land of Ice,\Nmy body wouldn't stop trembling.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.89,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had never dreamed I'd get to see\Nthat legend with my own two eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a zombie creator's--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Cindry-chan! Why are\Nyou walking in front of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.90,0:05:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet another legend shall come back to life!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.86,0:05:41.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, No. 900.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.99,0:05:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time for him to awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.93,0:05:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is the only berserker to have\Ngone down in history as a "Devil."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:06:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oars!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.12,0:06:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Awakening After 500 Years!!\NOars Opens His Eyes!!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get this underway!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that? A-A giant's... corpse?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.34,0:07:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for a giant, it's freaking huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.27,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make a sound, Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.11,0:07:43.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be still, Straw Hat Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am your new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about to provide you with a voice and body
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that you may live as a zombie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.80,0:08:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget all of your past relations\Nand become my obedient soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.41,0:08:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.02,0:08:15.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should have made Cindry-chan\Nagree to forget her past, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.94,0:08:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'd actually get to eat on plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could break your knee caps like plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.99,0:08:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes! Cindry-chan, that threat was super scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.74,0:08:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cindry doesn't show Hogback\Nany mercy, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a Hog-smackdown...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.36,0:08:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time! Awaken!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.29,0:08:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Luffy's shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arise from 500 years of slumber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.40,0:09:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy's shadow...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.77,0:09:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went in!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.28,0:10:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.34,0:11:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.29,0:11:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-Crap! They found us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I screamed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.37,0:11:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A demon has awoken!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kumacy! Don't tell me\Nyou've been sheltering the pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My bride! What are you doing down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magnificent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:13:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How truly overawing!\NHe's a piece of art! A real devil!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.08,0:13:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.19,0:13:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:43.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.30,0:13:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kumacy, don't let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.03,0:13:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Okay!\N--What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.91,0:14:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Now zoom!\N--Yep!\N--Uh-huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.25,0:14:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Where are the pirates?\NWhere did my bride go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.76,0:14:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They ran as fast as their legs could carry them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.26,0:14:17.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, can they run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.57,0:14:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tch! I won't let them escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.93,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji, feed me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.36,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Sanji? Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that? What did we just witness?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The corpse started to move\Nafter he inserted Luffy's shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the deal behind these zombies.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.39,0:15:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how Dr. Hogback\Nbrings people back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.42,0:15:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That huge creep's ability probably stems from...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.64,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...a Devil Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Considering the first word out\Nof his mouth was "meat"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that monstrous giant clearly\Nhas Luffy's personality, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yeah...\N--Then think back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ran into a penguin in the\Nbreezeway who resembled Sanji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't kick a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:29.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it kills me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.83,0:15:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! So does that mean\Nhe had Sanji's shadow?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.45,0:15:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was the samurai who hit\Nus with the back of his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.97,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I see your panties?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.43,0:15:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.89,0:15:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Brook's shadow! And we had no idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.06,0:15:58.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of the strange things on this\Nisland are starting to make sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.86,0:16:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was just pretending to make zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.51,0:16:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man is making a mockery of human life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.99,0:16:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this fulfilling "mankind's dream"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.65,0:16:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "resurrecting the dead"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.46,0:16:16.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Hogback is a truly\Nwonderful man! I respect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't the least bit\Ninterested in saving people!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just a scumbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.06,0:16:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.43,0:16:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have time to lament over that now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our pals fell victim to his\Ngame of make-believe zombies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.44,0:16:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see? We're the\Nonly ones who can save them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.11,0:16:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry! They carried\NLuffy's body down this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.53,0:16:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right! The perv said to take him to the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he meant Sunny.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Zoro and Sanji met the same fate,\Nwe might find them there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.50,0:16:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, those guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.10,0:16:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can be such a handful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.81,0:17:21.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Chopper!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.13,0:17:44.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.11,0:17:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This freak... is really strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.52,0:17:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Care to say your last farewells?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.57,0:18:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is going to marry me today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moron! If I can't protect a single woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.87,0:18:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there was no point in being born a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.46,0:18:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Usopp, that weapon--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.11,0:18:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why does Usopp have it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.62,0:18:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.95,0:18:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Six Chamber Viper Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.27,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's vanishing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.78,0:18:44.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I'm disappearing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.32,0:18:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.96,0:18:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami vanished with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.54,0:18:59.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.75,0:19:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.67,0:19:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some strong odor is masking his scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me, Usopp! Cho--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.38,0:19:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Nami! What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me, Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.55,0:19:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zombies, I'll let you take over from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.88,0:19:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catch those two and bring\Nthem before Moria-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.90,0:19:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot! Which direction\Nis his voice coming from?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.66,0:19:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?! A zombie in armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of zombies are downstairs, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this looks bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.98,0:19:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've got a bunch of zombies upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.27,0:20:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, pirates! Hand over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.94,0:20:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chopper, don't get caught!\NThey'll take our shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.87,0:20:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.67,0:20:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your shadows...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is even a zombie painting!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.01,0:20:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.00,0:20:32.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You guys play dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're immortal and get to\Nattack in numbers! It's no fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's low! Aw, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.77,0:20:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we want is your shadow, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap! Let go! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.28,0:21:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them catch us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.07,0:21:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's more?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.55,0:21:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fork over your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us your shadows!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.04,0:21:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grah! W-We... We're doomed...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.21,0:21:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, someone else is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.10,0:22:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our buddies are getting purified!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better get your mitts...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.83,0:22:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...off my sworn little brothers, punks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Certainly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.70,0:22:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck are those guys?\NThey're rottin' bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.81,0:22:44.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.74,0:22:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we take too long? We're short one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:23:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, Chopper, are you two all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.54,0:23:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're my shadow,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.99,0:23:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,why don't you understand\Nhow important this afro is?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.33,0:23:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is a reason why I can't afford to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my afro! Anything but the 'fro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.43,0:23:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.01,0:23:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Belief Worth Begging to Live For!!\NBrook Defends His Afro!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.60,0:23:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
